column2:
For example, if using terminal:
curl --request POST \
  --url https://preview.api.climatiq.io/travel/v1-preview1/distance \
  --header "Authorization: Bearer $CLIMATIQ_API_KEY" \
  --data '{
    "origin": {
        "locode": "DE-HAM"
    },
    "destination": {
        "query": "Berlin"
    },
    "travel_mode": "car",
    "car_details": {
        "car_type": "plugin_hybrid"
   }
}'
